sentences: Shiori Tamai (玉井 詩織, Tamai Shiori, born June 4, 1995) is a Japanese idol, a member of the girl group Momoiro Clover Z. As of December 2012, she is currently voice acting in the Nippon Television series Akumu-chan as a personage from the dreams of Keiko Kitagawa's character.
